Approach 1

class Solution {
    public boolean isPowerOfTwo(int n) {
        if(n <= 0) return false;
        while(n%2 == 0) {
            n /= 2; 
        }

        return n == 1;
    }
}

Approach 2

class Solution {
    public boolean isPowerOfTwo(int n) {
        if(n <= 0) return false;
        return ((n & n-1) == 0);
    }
}

Time Complexity : O(1)
Space Complexity : O(1)
